snippet.title: Relationship Advocates
snippet.description:
Hi! Welcome to the Channel. My name is Charan. 
This Channel is dedicated to encouraging people to get in to and stay in relationships.
We do this by showing you what real relationships are really like. You can think of this channel 
as the only resource in the world were you can actually learn what relationships involve. This way you know what 
to expect as normal. Never give up on your relationship. If are having relationship problems you cannot solve.....dont give up..email me and ill help you work things out.
